cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.AR 

The paper discusses techniques for optimizing Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) for low-power mobile and embedded devices. This topic is primarily related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), as well as neural networks (cs.NE) and robotics (cs.AR) which often involve the use of CNNs.
